application.editor

Class Editor

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.editor.Editor

  • public final class Editor
extends java.lang.Object
    The Editor class controls the dynamic editing of a parsed Handy Andy work order. The primary editor takes the form of a JavaFX accordion. Changes made within the accordion are instantly rendered out into an output PDDocument which is also viewed as part of the editor.
